abstract.text: Interact with groups of related functionality that Matter accessories expose.

legalNotices.copyright: Copyright © 2025 Apple Inc. All rights reserved.

inlineContent.text: A cluster defines data and a set of related commands that operate on that data. For example, a temperature sensor exposes the Temperature Measurement cluster that provides ambient temperature. A door lock exposes the Door Lock cluster that provides the state of the lock, as well as commands to lock, unlock, and add access codes.

abstract.text: Communicate with and control smart home devices from a variety of manufacturers.
